data.description: Farm home was totally redone in 1996 and remodeled and added on to in 2018.  Home offers an eat in kitchen, dining room, living room, den, and primary bed room on the main level. Primary suite access to a small deck and offers a beautiful bath with tub and shower. Finishing off the main level are two more bedrooms and a full bath and nice sized laundry room.  Upstairs offers another bedroom and a sitting area full bath and a playroom that could be used as a 5th bedroom.
